title: [Rumor Woods, Canine Track]
[Rumor Woods, Equid Track]
description: A scattered group of tree stumps sits on either side of the viewing stands, each one stained a bright crimson, then adorned with a shield engraved with the image of an ebon wolf.  Well-used horseshoes weigh down the shields, although the muddied grass beneath appears to have a firm hold regardless of assistance.  The sounds of clashing metal dance together with the murmurs of market noise coming from the southwest.
